SUMMARY:WordPress News Night
DESCRIPTION:WordPress Lancaster\nIt's WordPress News Night! Join us as we 
 catch up on the latest happenings in the WordPress world. We'll cover a wi
 de range of topics including:\n\n* **WordPress 7.0** — What's new\, what
 's changed\, and what it means for your sites\n* **EmDash** — A new Word
 Press "like" CMS from Cloudflare. Is this the future? Or just another open
  source CMS?\n* **AI-powered themes and plugins** — How AI is being used
  to generate custom WordPress themes and plugins\, and what that means for
  builders\n* Plus other news and announcements from the WordPress ecosyste
 m\n\nWhether you're a developer\, designer\, site owner\, or just curious 
 about where WordPress is headed\, this is a great one to attend. Bring you
 r questions and opinions!\nPizza 🍕 and introductions at 7pm. Come with 
 your laptops and join the discussion.\n\n📍 About our location\n\n* Free
  parking in lot off of market street. [See here for directions to The Cand
 y Factory\, Warehouse D](https://goo.gl/maps/2NFNcZFxQC1qi8M66).
